(VERSION 1.1) (22 December 2009)

DE_Tudor_Xmas, a map by The Wormhole Studios



The same map as "DE_Tudor_TWS" (http://www.fpsbanana.com/maps/116857) but now in christmas style !



-------------------------------
INSTALL
-------------------------------

1. Put the files "DE_Tudor_Xmas_v2.bsp" & "DE_Tudor_Xmas_2v.nav" here:
"C:\Programs\Steam\SteamApps\1245780\counter-strike source\cstrike\maps"

2. Start up Counter-Strike: Source and play DE_Tudor_Xmas !

-------------------------------
CREDITS
-------------------------------
